Prison break map. Play it. Have fun.

Tactical Situation:

 Suspects have robbed a bank in North Hollywood. They wounded several civilians, detonated an explosive and are preparing an escape from the bank. SWAT has arrived now and will try to neutralize the suspects.

Terrorists:

 Make your way to the white truck at the end of the road ("A" on your radar), 3 blocks far away. If you reach the escape point all CTs will be eliminated and you win. Or simply eliminate all CTs. -16 Spawnpoints in the bank.

Counter-Terrorists:

 You must prevent the Ts from fleeing to the white truck ("A" on the radar). If ANY suspect can reach this escape point all CTs will get killed and the terrorists win. Neutralize them all. -16 spawnpoints in total at 2 APCs Note: I made an ESCAPE map, so the bomb is not important!!! After all i should even mention that this map is an attempt to recreate the tactical situation of the so called "North Hollywood Shootout". Watch a movie about the "North Hollywood Shootout" An extraction from wikipedia.org: "The North Hollywood shootout was an armed confrontation between two heavily-armed and armored bank robbers (Larry Eugene Phillips, Jr. and Emil Dechebal Matasareanu) and patrol and SWAT officers of the Los Angeles Police Department (LAPD) on February 28, 1997, at a Bank of America teller-office. The shootout resulted in the wounding of fourteen people (twelve police officers and two civilians) and the deaths of both bank robbers. Although only the suspects were killed, the sheer number of injuries made this one of the bloodiest single cases of violent crime in the 1990s, and one of the most significant single bank robberies of the 20th century." Final Notes: Of course this is not 1:1 but some key locations may look a lot like on the publicly available TV reports, documents etc. while other elements are completely fictional but tactically interesting... So mainly this map focusses on playability issues. All in all i find it a easy to learn and challenging map. Hope you enjoy it too! the map was made by me, foxconn SO report bugs, errors, feedback to jpdelacruz@web.de

UPDATED:

Well, too much has been added to say. There's a few building sections added and a lot has been tweeked.


Evaporated the fur, because it covers them. If you only knew the plans they had for us.


Ok, so I only took a few screenies (but there is a great deal more to this map). It is centered around a parking structure with two floors, 4 cameras (3 from inside a defendable shack on the top floor), a sliding garage door that can only be accessed from inside (teamwork is crucial; have teammates watch the cameras and work the door to help out humans; or be selfish and just defend the upper level).

There is also a 3 story appliance store, with a defendable show-room (with camera and backdoor), an upper lounge, and an upper-upper patio. Beside the store, there is a large traffic wreck with plenty of fire and a decent (read; FAIR) camp spot. 

Beside this, is an office building that is still in construction (by that I mean, the upper floor is littered with boxes and mess, while the bottom floor is a bit more officey).

And finally, there is a maze of suburbia with a few camp spots. It's medium sized map that tested well (in previous versions; this is the newest, and so far untested vesion). So, enjoy and play fair.

Ok. Me and my firend Colors where playing DeathRun for a few days ago and we thought it was pretty fun. So we created our own edit of DeathRun called ExplosiveRun

Ok im sure you wonder how you play it. here it is

Everyone starts at the same spawn without any gun. NOT EVEN A KNIFE. They have to jump over explosive barrels that have a detonator that will detonate them in 20 sec. If they survive they will enter a few corridors. Each corridor sets in to flames every 3rd sec so you have to be fast. And its some breakable floors to that you can get traped in and burn to death.
After the corridors you have to be first up to a wagon that contaions one and only one ak47. The guy who gets it will be able to shoot everybody else to death and if he dont the whole map will be set into flames in 20 sec and everyone will die.

It's really funny. I didnt thought that it was that fun untill i played it. I laghed all the time. Its perfect to play with your mates or have on your server.

I think we are the first who does this kind of map so i've made my own category called explosive run = eprun

It's recommended to use NOBLOCK when your playing this. Otherwise you wont be able to take the lead when you at last. And if you dont use noblock you might be blocked and die.!!

edm_warzones is a Counter-Strike Source map. It is a collection of aim maps set in 4 different warzones. One person gets to decide at the beginning of the round which one to go to and everyone goes there for the round.

It doesn't support bots.

In an edm map both teams spawn in sealed areas, one person is allowed out and gets to pick which area to teleport everyone to. Each of these areas are in the style of an aim map.

If you download it and enjoy it, please comment.

Thankyou.
